# LBT-T300 Buffer Overflow

Vulnerability description: LBT-T300-T310 v2.2.3.6 of Shenzhen Rio Tinto Technology Co., Ltd. was found to have a buffer overflow at/appy.cgi through multiple parameters.

### 1.username_3g

#### Vulnerability analysis

Due to the lack of data length restrictions of the username_3g parameter in function config_3g_para, a buffer overflow vulnerability is created.

function call chain Main()->start3g_main()->config_3g_para().

![1.png](/Users/fly/Desktop/img/1.png)
